
  CS-734, Hardware Practicum
  Syllabus

  Note:  Schedule is approximate.

  Weeks   Activity
  1-2     Consult with faculty member to lay out scope of proposed
          project and prepare written proposal and development plan.

  2-5     Perform pilot work necessary to insure the project is
          feasable.  Revise proposal and development plan if necessary.

  6-14    Implement project, consulting weekly with faculty member to
          assess progress.

  15      Write report documenting project design and implementation.

  Text: There is no text for the course.  Students will consult
  documentation specific to their individaual projects.

  
